1
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:45,180
[My Heroic Husband]

2
00:01:46,470 --> 00:01:47,980
[Episode 33]

3
00:03:15,090 --> 00:03:17,069
Ning Yi.

4
00:03:17,810 --> 00:03:19,510
Get out!

5
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:21,810
Holy Master,

6
00:03:21,810 --> 00:03:24,630
I'm afraid we're losing the fortress of Xuanwei Camp.

7
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:25,690
Holy Master,

8
00:03:25,690 --> 00:03:28,130
East Gate and West Gate have both been occupied by their armies.

9
00:03:28,130 --> 00:03:29,169
Master,

10
00:03:29,169 --> 00:03:30,530
North Gate was lost.

11
00:03:30,530 --> 00:03:34,209
Dong Dao Fu and his vice generals have already entered the city.

12
00:03:34,209 --> 00:03:37,150
Now that they want to die with us, why don't we allow them to?

13
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:39,090
Gather all our people at the powder magazine.

14
00:03:39,090 --> 00:03:41,090
Yes! Yes! Yes!

15
00:03:41,090 --> 00:03:42,489
Go!

16
00:03:42,489 --> 00:03:43,989
Master,

17
00:03:43,989 --> 00:03:45,169
go find Xi Gua.

18
00:03:45,169 --> 00:03:46,489
Send her out of the city at all costs.

19
00:03:46,489 --> 00:03:48,869
Master, hurry up and go!

20
00:03:49,729 --> 00:03:51,229
Yes.

21
00:03:51,769 --> 00:03:53,369
Ya!

22
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,190
[Badao Camp]

23
00:04:13,549 --> 00:04:14,489
How's the situation out there?

24
00:04:14,489 --> 00:04:16,311
Dong Dao Fu's army has entered the city.

25
00:04:16,311 --> 00:04:18,869
Holy Master has sent a signal to gather all the people at the powder magazine.

26
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:21,349
How could they attack at this time? All right.

27
00:04:21,349 --> 00:04:22,289
Go gather our people!

28
00:04:22,289 --> 00:04:24,289
Yes!

29
00:04:24,289 --> 00:04:27,369
Xi Gua, the Holy Master ordered you to go to the powder magazine,

30
00:04:27,369 --> 00:04:29,530
because he wants a cluster suicide.

31
00:04:29,530 --> 00:04:32,310
We're about to lose Lin'an. Don't seek your doom.

32
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,630
I have to go, too!

33
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:35,750
I have to go save the Holy Master.

34
00:04:40,609 --> 00:04:42,188
Hurry! Hurry! Open the door!

35
00:04:42,188 --> 00:04:43,429
Get all the gunpowder out!

36
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:45,230
Let's confront them!

37
00:04:58,589 --> 00:05:01,929
What... What... Why are there so many holes in the roof?

38
00:05:01,929 --> 00:05:02,929
Holy Master.

39
00:05:02,929 --> 00:05:05,229
All the drains are blocked.

40
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:11,609
Brother.

41
00:05:11,609 --> 00:05:13,929
This gunpowder is useless now.

42
00:05:15,029 --> 00:05:17,010
Fang Tian Lei!

43
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:33,610
Leader, we've gathered all the people.

44
00:05:33,610 --> 00:05:34,989
We're ready to go now.

45
00:05:34,989 --> 00:05:36,570
Okay, follow me.

46
00:05:36,570 --> 00:05:38,850
Let's go find them in the powder magazine.

47
00:05:38,850 --> 00:05:40,550
You can't go!

48
00:05:43,570 --> 00:05:45,348
A'Sha, you protect Counselor Ning.

49
00:05:45,348 --> 00:05:47,270
He is not good at fighting. Keep him safe.

50
00:05:47,270 --> 00:05:49,788
No matter what happens, find a way to get him out of the city.

51
00:05:49,789 --> 00:05:51,189
Yes.

52
00:06:00,249 --> 00:06:01,609
Fang Tian Lei,

53
00:06:01,609 --> 00:06:04,010
are you content with this gift I prepared for you?

54
00:06:04,010 --> 00:06:05,169
Not bad.

55
00:06:05,169 --> 00:06:06,970
I was looking for a good fight with you.

56
00:06:06,970 --> 00:06:09,350
Yet you came without invitation.

57
00:06:09,350 --> 00:06:10,629
Xi Gua!

58
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:12,830
How's the Holy Master?

59
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:15,629
Holy Master has ordered all people of the Badao Camp

60
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:17,770
to send Liu Xi Gua out of the city without delay.

61
00:06:17,770 --> 00:06:18,929
Yes.

62
00:06:18,929 --> 00:06:19,850
I won't leave.

63
00:06:19,850 --> 00:06:21,049
I'm going to the gunpowder magazine to save Holy Master.

64
00:06:21,049 --> 00:06:22,449
No.

65
00:06:22,449 --> 00:06:25,010
Dong Dao Fu's army will come here soon. I can't let anything happen to you.

66
00:06:25,010 --> 00:06:26,429
Let go of me!

67
00:06:26,429 --> 00:06:28,729
- Let go of me!
- Xi Gua!

68
00:06:29,589 --> 00:06:31,889
That's all the manpower in Lin'an.

69
00:06:31,889 --> 00:06:33,949
Holy Master wants me to protect you.

70
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:35,129
I have to send you out.

71
00:06:35,129 --> 00:06:36,489
He is my uncle.

72
00:06:36,489 --> 00:06:37,809
I have to save him.

73
00:06:37,809 --> 00:06:39,709
Liu Xi Gua!

74
00:06:42,970 --> 00:06:44,670
Take her away.

75
00:07:15,970 --> 00:07:17,050
You go and join Xi Gua.

76
00:07:17,050 --> 00:07:18,570
No. We'll leave together.

77
00:07:18,570 --> 00:07:20,289
I'll be worried if Chen Fan protects her by himself.

78
00:07:20,289 --> 00:07:22,968
You're going to protect Xi Gua even if you have to sacrifice yourself. Do you hear me?

79
00:07:22,968 --> 00:07:24,249
- Zheng Biao!
- Yes!

80
00:07:24,249 --> 00:07:26,069
Make your way out with Fang Qiong.

81
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:26,869
Yes.

82
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:28,270
Go!

83
00:07:29,530 --> 00:07:31,148
Fang Qiong, go!

84
00:07:31,149 --> 00:07:32,449
Go!

85
00:07:52,770 --> 00:07:54,270
Wang Jin.

86
00:07:58,630 --> 00:08:00,729
Holy Master, hurry up and go!

87
00:08:02,970 --> 00:08:05,070
Wang Jin!

88
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:08,930
Dong Dao Fu! I will kill you!

89
00:08:08,930 --> 00:08:10,429
Dong Dao Fu!

90
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:13,129
I will kill you!

91
00:08:17,469 --> 00:08:19,450
Bring the traitor Fang Tian Lei

92
00:08:19,450 --> 00:08:20,989
back to Wudu for trial.

93
00:08:20,990 --> 00:08:22,490
Yes!

94
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:26,770
[South Gate]

95
00:08:36,570 --> 00:08:38,170
Stop!

96
00:08:45,489 --> 00:08:47,289
Stay put.

97
00:08:53,889 --> 00:08:55,749
Who are in the carriage?

98
00:09:00,450 --> 00:09:02,150
Let them pass.

99
00:09:18,649 --> 00:09:21,628
This black powder can't be used after it's soaked in water.

100
00:09:21,629 --> 00:09:23,930
These and those... are all soaked in water.

101
00:09:23,930 --> 00:09:25,130
What are we supposed to do?

102
00:09:25,130 --> 00:09:26,949
Yes. There was heavy rain.

103
00:09:26,950 --> 00:09:28,549
Fang Tian Lei has no gunpowder to use.

104
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:29,828
But we don't, either.

105
00:09:29,829 --> 00:09:31,329
Yes.

106
00:09:55,770 --> 00:09:59,188
Lady Lou, it's safe outside temporarily. You'd better leave now.

107
00:10:11,889 --> 00:10:13,830
It's safe outside. Let's get out of here.

108
00:10:13,830 --> 00:10:16,108
Let's go now! Go.

109
00:10:17,310 --> 00:10:19,010
Leave!

110
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:08,210
[Suburb of Lin'an]

111
00:11:08,210 --> 00:11:10,729
Don't be afraid. I will not kill you.

112
00:11:10,729 --> 00:11:12,228
We'll just use your place for now.

113
00:11:12,229 --> 00:11:13,868
Take them away after they're tied up.

114
00:11:13,869 --> 00:11:15,169
Yes.

115
00:11:20,390 --> 00:11:23,630
- You two go up there to look out.
- Is Madame settled in?

116
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:24,708
Yes.

117
00:11:24,709 --> 00:11:26,828
After the wedding ceremony, Holy Master asked us to escort Madame

118
00:11:26,829 --> 00:11:28,588
and leave the city in disguise through the South Gate.

119
00:11:28,589 --> 00:11:31,209
I have arranged for her to live in a cottage in the far outskirts of Lin'an.

120
00:11:31,209 --> 00:11:32,609
Some guards were left to serve her.

121
00:11:32,609 --> 00:11:35,750
No one will find out her identity. Don't worry.

122
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:40,509
So it seems Master has long expected Dong Dao Fu will attack the city.

123
00:11:41,930 --> 00:11:44,989
But since it was already expected,

124
00:11:46,409 --> 00:11:49,689
why does it only take some rain,

125
00:11:49,689 --> 00:11:52,629
just a night's rain, to defeat us?

126
00:11:52,629 --> 00:11:57,549
And why did the guards at the South Gate

127
00:11:57,549 --> 00:12:00,370
let us pass so easily?

128
00:12:04,889 --> 00:12:07,530
Lin'an has a lot of rainfall.

129
00:12:07,530 --> 00:12:09,689
Here it comes again.

130
00:12:09,689 --> 00:12:11,390
Yes.

131
00:12:12,950 --> 00:12:15,509
This rain comes too fast.

132
00:12:23,970 --> 00:12:27,890
I have to help him to win the battle in Lin'an.

133
00:12:27,890 --> 00:12:29,910
What if you can't win?

134
00:12:31,450 --> 00:12:33,150
No way.

135
00:12:34,910 --> 00:12:36,869
It can't be him.

136
00:12:40,450 --> 00:12:42,050
It can't be him.

137
00:12:42,050 --> 00:12:43,509
No.

138
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:47,409
Xi Gua, what's wrong? Don't scare me.

139
00:12:48,009 --> 00:12:50,429
Are you worried about the Holy Master?

140
00:12:50,429 --> 00:12:52,470
You can remove your worries.

141
00:12:52,470 --> 00:12:55,269
Madame has already settled down.

142
00:12:55,269 --> 00:12:56,990
Holy Master...

143
00:13:01,970 --> 00:13:04,450
He will come back safely, too.

144
00:13:07,330 --> 00:13:09,130
Why...

145
00:13:12,230 --> 00:13:14,529
did we lose?

146
00:13:18,810 --> 00:13:20,410
Why?

147
00:14:10,170 --> 00:14:12,650
So, you work for the Secret Investigation Department?

148
00:14:14,070 --> 00:14:15,770
Am I right?

149
00:14:20,649 --> 00:14:22,249
Yes.

150
00:14:25,989 --> 00:14:29,049
Do you know how my father died?

151
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:33,190
After this battle is finished,

152
00:14:33,869 --> 00:14:35,789
don't go to save the Holy Master,

153
00:14:36,529 --> 00:14:38,550
no matter what.

154
00:14:40,050 --> 00:14:42,470
These are all the people you have now.

155
00:14:43,589 --> 00:14:46,309
Don't lose the whole Badao Camp.

156
00:15:10,769 --> 00:15:13,690
From the moment you came to Badao Camp,

157
00:15:14,369 --> 00:15:17,029
you've never said anything true.

158
00:15:18,229 --> 00:15:20,110
You lied to me.

159
00:15:22,369 --> 00:15:25,069
Go for ten miles to the east,

160
00:15:25,069 --> 00:15:27,330
you'll see the camp of your enemy.

161
00:15:28,030 --> 00:15:30,190
There's some food behind the camp.

162
00:15:30,869 --> 00:15:33,169
If you steal some,

163
00:15:33,169 --> 00:15:35,369
you won't starve.

164
00:15:38,690 --> 00:15:40,090
Come back!

165
00:15:52,349 --> 00:15:54,729
You address me as "Your Ladyship."

166
00:15:57,649 --> 00:16:00,690
You said I could work for the people.

167
00:16:03,690 --> 00:16:06,749
You said you recognized what I did.

168
00:16:09,330 --> 00:16:12,609
You said you genuinely wanted to help me.

169
00:16:14,930 --> 00:16:17,170
I believed you

170
00:16:18,209 --> 00:16:22,129
because you did a lot of thinking and said so much to me.

171
00:16:23,629 --> 00:16:26,110
But is all this fake?

172
00:16:28,649 --> 00:16:31,369
Lin'an cannot go on like this anymore!

173
00:16:32,190 --> 00:16:34,530
The situation in the North is tense.

174
00:16:34,530 --> 00:16:37,789
If they lose this battle in Lin'an, the Wu Dynasty will be done for.

175
00:16:37,790 --> 00:16:39,710
None of my business!

176
00:16:39,710 --> 00:16:41,170
And it has nothing to do with Badao Camp.

177
00:16:41,170 --> 00:16:43,570
It's none of my business, either!

178
00:16:45,950 --> 00:16:47,550
I admit it.

179
00:16:49,210 --> 00:16:51,690
Since I came to the Badao Camp,

180
00:16:53,609 --> 00:16:56,330
all that I said was fake.

181
00:16:58,430 --> 00:17:01,129
I did everything for you

182
00:17:02,810 --> 00:17:05,590
to achieve my own purpose.

183
00:17:09,090 --> 00:17:11,369
These things are true.

184
00:17:13,169 --> 00:17:15,290
But my friendship with you

185
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:18,689
and your buddies

186
00:17:19,369 --> 00:17:21,390
is also true.

187
00:17:29,530 --> 00:17:31,969
In the long history,

188
00:17:33,350 --> 00:17:37,130
there are too many people who rose in revolt like you.

189
00:17:38,929 --> 00:17:40,490
I don't want to see you become

190
00:17:40,490 --> 00:17:44,110
one of those cold figures in the history books.

191
00:17:50,950 --> 00:17:52,650
But...

192
00:17:55,050 --> 00:17:57,729
But why you?

193
00:17:57,729 --> 00:18:00,150
Ning Yi,

194
00:18:01,290 --> 00:18:04,090
why did you lie to me?

195
00:18:04,090 --> 00:18:08,250
Why do you work for the Secret Investigation Department?

196
00:18:09,609 --> 00:18:11,889
My father...

197
00:18:11,889 --> 00:18:16,709
My father was killed by the people from the Secret Investigation Department.

198
00:18:17,570 --> 00:18:19,989
I shall take revenge!

199
00:18:21,490 --> 00:18:23,508
I will avenge his death!

200
00:18:23,509 --> 00:18:25,689
Ning Yi,

201
00:18:30,969 --> 00:18:33,530
I will not forgive you!

202
00:18:40,290 --> 00:18:44,010
I will not forgive you!

203
00:18:50,169 --> 00:18:51,769
Liu Xi Gua.

204
00:18:53,789 --> 00:18:54,810
Liu Xi Gua.

205
00:18:54,810 --> 00:18:56,989
Get out!

206
00:19:18,770 --> 00:19:22,029
I will not forgive you.

207
00:20:21,290 --> 00:20:26,429
From the moment you come to Badao Camp, you won't have any say.

208
00:20:26,430 --> 00:20:30,090
I want you to be my Army Advisor, so you'll have to be.

209
00:20:32,730 --> 00:20:35,009
I heard you wanted to flee.

210
00:20:35,009 --> 00:20:36,389
What's wrong?

211
00:20:36,390 --> 00:20:38,969
Do you feel wronged being my army advisor?

212
00:20:42,269 --> 00:20:45,250
As long as you do what you promised, I'll give you the whole Badao Camp,

213
00:20:45,250 --> 00:20:48,150
let alone a group of my people.

214
00:20:51,010 --> 00:20:53,470
If you want to call me Xi Gua,

215
00:20:53,470 --> 00:20:55,750
I don't mind it, either.

216
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:58,730
As long as you are not my enemy, I will be fine with anything.

217
00:20:58,730 --> 00:21:00,769
A'Sha, you protect the army advisor.

218
00:21:00,769 --> 00:21:02,570
He is not good at fighting. Keep him safe.

219
00:21:02,570 --> 00:21:06,230
No matter what happens, you have to send him out of the city.

220
00:21:12,390 --> 00:21:13,869
Ning Yi,

221
00:21:13,869 --> 00:21:16,269
don't let her down!

222
00:21:16,269 --> 00:21:18,709
Can you do it?

223
00:21:18,709 --> 00:21:20,870
He can, Aunt.

224
00:21:49,580 --> 00:21:53,300
[Tomb of Bao Wen Han]

225
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:07,420
[Tomb of Lou Shu Heng]

226
00:22:16,430 --> 00:22:19,069
Lady Lou, the cart is overloaded.

227
00:22:19,069 --> 00:22:21,550
We'd better leave this box of books here.

228
00:22:26,260 --> 00:22:28,089
This is the map drawn by Leader Bao.

229
00:22:28,089 --> 00:22:32,060
It shows where the outlaws in the Wu Dynasty are hiding.

230
00:22:34,710 --> 00:22:35,888
Keep it.

231
00:22:35,888 --> 00:22:37,300
Yes.

232
00:22:39,580 --> 00:22:42,060
Come and load the cart.

233
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:54,430
[Lin'an]

234
00:22:54,430 --> 00:22:57,129
Dong Dao Fu has eliminated all eight camps of bandits.

235
00:22:57,129 --> 00:22:59,609
Holy Master Fang Tian Lei was taken alive.

236
00:22:59,609 --> 00:23:03,510
Lin'an has become peaceful again.

237
00:23:04,180 --> 00:23:07,280
[Fang]

238
00:23:11,360 --> 00:23:13,150
[Wu]

239
00:23:13,150 --> 00:23:17,168
Great, great!

240
00:23:17,168 --> 00:23:19,690
Move! Move! Make way!

241
00:23:23,630 --> 00:23:24,410
Serves you right!

242
00:23:24,410 --> 00:23:25,970
This is what you deserve.

243
00:23:25,970 --> 00:23:27,400
Finally! Relief!

244
00:23:37,990 --> 00:23:38,809
Take your medicine.

245
00:23:38,809 --> 00:23:39,710
You're welcome.

246
00:23:40,750 --> 00:23:45,140
Heat this medicine with three bowls of water and condense it into one bowl.

247
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:06,260
Kneel down!

248
00:24:14,190 --> 00:24:15,548
General,

249
00:24:15,548 --> 00:24:18,369
the bandits around the city have all been eliminated or captured.

250
00:24:18,369 --> 00:24:19,768
The leader of the bandits, Fang Tian Lei, has been captured.

251
00:24:19,768 --> 00:24:21,389
He has been put in prison.

252
00:24:21,389 --> 00:24:24,429
After I check all the gunpowder and weapons, we're ready to return to the capital.

253
00:24:24,429 --> 00:24:25,990
Good.

254
00:24:25,990 --> 00:24:28,189
What about the gunpowder?

255
00:24:28,189 --> 00:24:31,049
Thanks to the rainproof lining, the black powder, and the gunfire

256
00:24:31,049 --> 00:24:34,589
in the grain hopper have been preserved intact.

257
00:24:34,589 --> 00:24:37,270
That's great!
[Badao Camp]

258
00:24:38,900 --> 00:24:41,700
[Wude Camp]

259
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:47,060
[Badao Camp]

260
00:24:53,690 --> 00:24:58,360
Fathe, we only became the richest people here for one day.

261
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:03,090
How about you borrow 30 cash from Tan'er?

262
00:25:03,090 --> 00:25:04,768
Let's use it to pay for the buns first.

263
00:25:04,768 --> 00:25:07,889
I don't want to. It's embarrassing.

264
00:25:07,889 --> 00:25:10,849
At that time, we even told him we were the Su family from Jiangning.

265
00:25:10,849 --> 00:25:12,909
How humiliating it would be if people knew it!

266
00:25:12,909 --> 00:25:15,349
Well, we can go together.

267
00:25:15,349 --> 00:25:16,928
I can't tell you what to do now, can I?

268
00:25:16,928 --> 00:25:19,508
General Dong, Lord Commander.

269
00:25:19,508 --> 00:25:22,069
Don't mind the courtesy. Go back to your work.

270
00:25:28,300 --> 00:25:29,950
Soldiers!

271
00:25:29,950 --> 00:25:34,068
These guys are the ones who saved Lin'an. They're our heroes.

272
00:25:34,068 --> 00:25:37,429
Please don't. Don't call us like that!

273
00:25:37,429 --> 00:25:38,590
We'll feel embarrassed.

274
00:25:38,590 --> 00:25:40,068
Yes, you flattered us.

275
00:25:40,068 --> 00:25:42,250
Just call us warriors.

276
00:25:42,250 --> 00:25:44,008
Warriors have always been praised since ancient times.

277
00:25:44,008 --> 00:25:45,388
Now we should praise the courage of scholars.

278
00:25:45,388 --> 00:25:48,688
Yes, it's a pity that we even missed Brother Ning's wedding.

279
00:25:48,688 --> 00:25:50,980
Yes, yes, yes.

280
00:25:51,890 --> 00:25:54,329
Go back to work, please.

281
00:25:54,329 --> 00:25:56,980
General, come on and take a look! The plaque has been hung up.

282
00:26:00,140 --> 00:26:01,429
Wude Camp.

283
00:26:01,429 --> 00:26:03,269
Great.

284
00:26:03,269 --> 00:26:05,569
Since the Wu Dynasty's Army came to Lin'an,

285
00:26:05,569 --> 00:26:09,750
the security and order of Lin'an have basically been restored now.

286
00:26:09,750 --> 00:26:14,090
Brother Ning, that is to say, your whole family is

287
00:26:14,090 --> 00:26:17,800
living under the nose of the bandits, yet they are still safe and sound.

288
00:26:17,800 --> 00:26:21,128
And you even came up with the idea to cover yourselves up,

289
00:26:21,128 --> 00:26:24,190
deceive everybody, and help me take back the city.

290
00:26:24,190 --> 00:26:25,729
Yes.

291
00:26:25,729 --> 00:26:28,850
Now that I think about it, it's quite incredible!

292
00:26:28,850 --> 00:26:33,330
When your army broke into the gates, I did have some concern.

293
00:26:33,330 --> 00:26:35,890
Before this, Lady Lu said

294
00:26:35,890 --> 00:26:39,089
you failed in the siege of the powder magazine.

295
00:26:39,089 --> 00:26:41,068
Your identity was almost exposed.

296
00:26:41,068 --> 00:26:45,730
I was kind of uncertain about today's attack.

297
00:26:45,730 --> 00:26:50,010
But in the end, I still chose to believe the person entrusted by Old Qin.

298
00:26:50,670 --> 00:26:51,949
General, come on.

299
00:26:51,949 --> 00:26:54,169
Allow me to introduce you.

300
00:26:54,169 --> 00:26:57,429
This is my wife, Su Tan'er.

301
00:26:57,429 --> 00:27:00,629
Tan'er, this is General Dong.

302
00:27:00,629 --> 00:27:02,770
Greetings to General Dong.

303
00:27:04,969 --> 00:27:09,810
Miss Xiao Chan also contributed greatly to this battle.

304
00:27:10,770 --> 00:27:12,249
Yes, of course.

305
00:27:12,249 --> 00:27:14,408
You've seen these four heroes.

306
00:27:14,408 --> 00:27:17,500
Like me, they are also matrilocal husbands.

307
00:27:18,710 --> 00:27:20,230
Nephew-in-law.

308
00:27:20,230 --> 00:27:21,308
I see.

309
00:27:21,308 --> 00:27:24,208
Lady Lu is not only the elite of the Secret Investigation Department,

310
00:27:24,208 --> 00:27:25,909
but also my martial arts teacher。

311
00:27:25,909 --> 00:27:26,709
I feel sorry.

312
00:27:26,709 --> 00:27:31,250
Without Lady Lu, I would have died many times.

313
00:27:31,250 --> 00:27:32,729
Yes, yes, I am...

314
00:27:32,729 --> 00:27:33,809
These are the people that

315
00:27:33,809 --> 00:27:34,710
I should introduce you to.

316
00:27:34,710 --> 00:27:36,068
That's pretty much all about it.

317
00:27:36,068 --> 00:27:39,328
General Dong, your time is valuable.

318
00:27:39,328 --> 00:27:40,810
Okay.

319
00:27:40,810 --> 00:27:42,989
I've met all the heroes.

320
00:27:42,989 --> 00:27:47,669
What I can't understand is you only have ten people in total.

321
00:27:47,669 --> 00:27:49,588
How did you do it?

322
00:27:49,588 --> 00:27:51,348
That's a long story.

323
00:27:51,348 --> 00:27:54,760
We shall start from the very beginning of this mission.

324
00:27:56,060 --> 00:27:57,790
It's empty.

325
00:28:00,300 --> 00:28:01,529
Oh, no.

326
00:28:01,529 --> 00:28:02,909
This is a trap.

327
00:28:02,909 --> 00:28:04,310
Let's go.

328
00:28:04,310 --> 00:28:08,588
We had planned everything that time, yet the gunpowder was gone.

329
00:28:08,588 --> 00:28:12,028
After that, we presumed that after the assassination, Fang Tian Lei

330
00:28:12,028 --> 00:28:16,270
had transferred all gunpowder and weapons.

331
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:20,149
Under the name of the Holy Master, now I order you two get married.

332
00:28:20,149 --> 00:28:21,889
The wedding ceremony will be held on the day after tomorrow.

333
00:28:21,889 --> 00:28:24,569
I killed a leader of the bandits, Bao Wen Han.

334
00:28:24,569 --> 00:28:28,610
Accidentally, I was ordered to marry Liu Xi Gua.

335
00:28:28,610 --> 00:28:31,149
At that time, there were only three days remaining

336
00:28:31,149 --> 00:28:33,068
before Master Qin would come to take the city.

337
00:28:33,068 --> 00:28:36,028
I'm well aware that Fang Tian Lei wouldn't trust me.

338
00:28:36,028 --> 00:28:38,208
The marriage must be for something else.

339
00:28:38,208 --> 00:28:41,680
So I could only go with his plan.

340
00:28:45,190 --> 00:28:47,068
I asked my teacher to follow Fang Tian Lei

341
00:28:47,069 --> 00:28:49,029
and Zheng Biao, the man in charge of the powder magazine.

342
00:28:49,029 --> 00:28:53,560
We found that they hid the gunpowder in the granary.

343
00:28:58,480 --> 00:29:00,290
How about it?

344
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,588
There was too much gunpowder.

345
00:29:04,588 --> 00:29:07,589
It would be impossible for just the few of us

346
00:29:07,589 --> 00:29:09,049
to transfer the gunpowder.

347
00:29:09,049 --> 00:29:12,780
I then came up with a plan with my wife.

348
00:29:14,780 --> 00:29:19,089
My dear. This is the grain hopper that the bandits used to store the gunpowder.

349
00:29:19,089 --> 00:29:22,249
I want you to help me make some waterproof linings.

350
00:29:22,249 --> 00:29:25,149
Make sure that the linings fit perfectly

351
00:29:25,150 --> 00:29:27,509
with the inner wall of the grain hopper and each peck of gunpowder

352
00:29:27,509 --> 00:29:30,669
so they will not go bad even if soaked in water.

353
00:29:35,150 --> 00:29:36,229
That's all?

354
00:29:36,229 --> 00:29:37,128
Yes.

355
00:29:37,128 --> 00:29:38,789
So simple?

356
00:29:38,789 --> 00:29:40,429
It's not simple, my dear.

357
00:29:40,429 --> 00:29:43,208
It's critical. You have to be very careful with it.

358
00:29:43,208 --> 00:29:45,329
Black powder will spoil when it touches water.

359
00:29:45,329 --> 00:29:47,430
If the gunpowder becomes useless, it could affect

360
00:29:47,430 --> 00:29:49,789
the safety of the civilians of the Wu Dynasty.

361
00:29:49,789 --> 00:29:50,989
I know.

362
00:29:50,989 --> 00:29:53,009
But it's still simple.

363
00:29:53,009 --> 00:29:54,268
Shall we make a bet?

364
00:29:54,268 --> 00:29:56,308
If a box of gunpowder is soaked in water,

365
00:29:56,308 --> 00:29:59,900
I'll do all the cooking from now on.

366
00:30:01,750 --> 00:30:03,720
I believe in you, my dear.

367
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:08,220
For the next few days, we have to work around the clock.

368
00:30:12,630 --> 00:30:16,520
Now, I'll teach you how to make waterproof cloth.

369
00:30:17,580 --> 00:30:18,429
This is the formula.

370
00:30:18,429 --> 00:30:20,490
Pass it around.

371
00:30:25,500 --> 00:30:28,050
The paint should be mixed evenly.

372
00:30:29,789 --> 00:30:32,150
Check it thoroughly.

373
00:30:32,150 --> 00:30:34,450
Use more paint.

374
00:30:35,100 --> 00:30:38,989
Fang Tian Lei had invited all eight camps to my wedding.

375
00:30:38,989 --> 00:30:41,828
He was luring me to send information out to you.

376
00:30:41,828 --> 00:30:42,989
Because there would be a weak defense,

377
00:30:42,989 --> 00:30:45,268
we could use this opportunity to attack the city.

378
00:30:45,268 --> 00:30:46,229
But in fact,

379
00:30:46,229 --> 00:30:49,149
that night was a good opportunity to deal with the powder magazine.

380
00:30:49,149 --> 00:30:50,868
I asked them to take advantage of this ceremony,

381
00:30:50,868 --> 00:30:55,028
and go to the granary with the waterproof linings when they changed shifts,

382
00:30:55,029 --> 00:30:58,788
and pad every grain hopper with the lining.

383
00:30:58,789 --> 00:31:00,750
Then we made some holes in the roof.

384
00:31:18,630 --> 00:31:19,429
Slow down, Father.

385
00:31:19,430 --> 00:31:20,548
Slow down.

386
00:31:20,549 --> 00:31:22,370
Be careful, Father.

387
00:31:23,470 --> 00:31:25,868
These kids are so rude.

388
00:31:25,868 --> 00:31:27,729
They don't have any respect for the old.

389
00:31:27,729 --> 00:31:29,950
Nor do they know how to love children.

390
00:31:29,950 --> 00:31:31,229
My son,

391
00:31:31,229 --> 00:31:32,550
you should recognize the reality.

392
00:31:32,550 --> 00:31:35,309
You are too old to be called young.

393
00:31:35,309 --> 00:31:37,530
You're not young anymore.

394
00:31:37,530 --> 00:31:38,469
Father,

395
00:31:38,469 --> 00:31:41,690
in your heart, I'll always be a child.

396
00:31:41,690 --> 00:31:43,508
Well. It's so dangerous here.

397
00:31:43,508 --> 00:31:44,629
Let's do it quickly.

398
00:31:44,629 --> 00:31:46,390
You're right.

399
00:31:46,390 --> 00:31:47,649
Here, Father, take this.

400
00:31:47,649 --> 00:31:48,980
Come on.

401
00:31:49,670 --> 00:31:52,349
Father, hold them tight.

402
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,609
Father.

403
00:31:54,609 --> 00:31:55,809
By the way, Gao.

404
00:31:55,809 --> 00:31:57,109
Brother Ning specifically instructed us not to

405
00:31:57,110 --> 00:31:59,008
lay water-proof cloth in those boxes by the door.

406
00:31:59,008 --> 00:32:00,749
No worries. I got it.

407
00:32:00,749 --> 00:32:03,469
Father, take my hands. Grab my hands, Father.

408
00:32:08,820 --> 00:32:12,730
When the big rain came, it looked like there was a flood.

409
00:32:20,390 --> 00:32:22,469
Why are there so many holes in this roof?

410
00:32:22,469 --> 00:32:23,648
Holy Master.

411
00:32:23,648 --> 00:32:25,348
The drains are all blocked.

412
00:32:25,348 --> 00:32:27,749
Fang Tian Lei thought all the gunpowder was soaked in water

413
00:32:27,749 --> 00:32:29,308
and couldn't be used anymore.

414
00:32:29,308 --> 00:32:30,990
Before they had time to check it carefully,

415
00:32:30,990 --> 00:32:32,850
General Dong then attacked the granary.

416
00:32:32,850 --> 00:32:36,520
He could only finish the fight against General Dong.

417
00:32:40,630 --> 00:32:44,069
General Dong. We were not introduced by him.

418
00:32:44,069 --> 00:32:47,770
I am Su Zhong Kan, the second master of the Su family.

419
00:32:47,770 --> 00:32:49,630
This is my son, Wen Xing.

420
00:32:49,630 --> 00:32:54,360
We're the ones who came up with this excellent plan.

421
00:32:55,150 --> 00:32:59,290
Apart from that, we used to test the feasibility of this plan.

422
00:32:59,290 --> 00:33:01,750
It always works. It's absolutely feasible.

423
00:33:01,750 --> 00:33:03,089
Yeah, yeah.

424
00:33:03,089 --> 00:33:04,229
How dare you say that.

425
00:33:04,229 --> 00:33:05,470
You finally admitted it now.

426
00:33:05,470 --> 00:33:06,769
It was all because of you.

427
00:33:06,769 --> 00:33:08,788
My lady lost all the Cloud Gauze in the storage.

428
00:33:08,788 --> 00:33:10,208
And it almost delayed the opening of the cloth store.

429
00:33:10,208 --> 00:33:12,370
All thanks to the Young Master.

430
00:33:14,750 --> 00:33:16,948
Xiao Chan, that's not fair.

431
00:33:16,948 --> 00:33:18,969
Yeah. That was ages ago.

432
00:33:18,969 --> 00:33:23,469
- Chan'er, you need… you need to let go of it.
- That's right.

433
00:33:23,469 --> 00:33:28,710
Uncle and cousin used this to fool the enemy.

434
00:33:28,710 --> 00:33:31,510
They've made amends for their fault.

435
00:33:31,510 --> 00:33:32,968
Tan'er is quite right!

436
00:33:32,968 --> 00:33:34,480
Yes, yes.

437
00:33:34,480 --> 00:33:37,660
General, sorry you have to see this.

438
00:33:37,660 --> 00:33:41,150
After that, Lady Lu asked me to attack the city when the rain fell.

439
00:33:41,150 --> 00:33:43,029
At that time I was extremely puzzled.

440
00:33:43,029 --> 00:33:46,750
Why could we only attack the city after the rain fell?

441
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:47,769
Now I finally understand it.

442
00:33:47,769 --> 00:33:52,768
You were protecting the gunpowder magazine under the guise of holding a wedding ceremony.

443
00:33:52,768 --> 00:33:53,788
Yes.

444
00:33:53,788 --> 00:33:57,809
Only in that way would Fang Tian Lei know that he had lost all of his advantages.

445
00:33:57,809 --> 00:34:00,930
Only then would they fight to the death against you.

446
00:34:00,930 --> 00:34:04,928
The Wu Dynasty is lucky to have you as the commander of the Secret Investigation Department.

447
00:34:04,928 --> 00:34:07,090
General, you flatter me.

448
00:34:10,770 --> 00:34:14,989
Lady Lu, the captivity name-list

449
00:34:14,989 --> 00:34:18,689
didn't mention anything about the adopted daughter of Fang Tian Lei.

450
00:34:18,689 --> 00:34:22,968
Yes, her people in Badao Camp have been quite chivalrous and righteous,

451
00:34:22,968 --> 00:34:24,389
and they were good to the people.

452
00:34:24,389 --> 00:34:27,090
The Secret Investigation Division has offered amnesty and enlistment to them.

453
00:34:28,209 --> 00:34:30,230
If they're really like what you said,

454
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:33,809
we can try to persuade her into working for the Secret Intelligence Division. That's great!

455
00:34:33,809 --> 00:34:36,550
It's just she is the adopted daughter of Fang.

456
00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:39,910
I'm afraid she will cause more trouble.

457
00:34:40,550 --> 00:34:44,588
Don't worry, General Dong. I will deal with it.

458
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:49,890
[Prision of Lin'an]

459
00:34:58,070 --> 00:35:00,009
Fang Tian Lei.

460
00:35:02,549 --> 00:35:07,070
Dong Dao Fu, if you still want to get something out of my mouth,

461
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:10,150
I suggest you forget about it.

462
00:35:10,150 --> 00:35:14,209
I am just doing my part as a comrade. I mean nothing else.

463
00:35:14,209 --> 00:35:17,930
You'll be questioned by someone else.

464
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:37,968
Ning Yi, I will rip you apart!

465
00:35:37,968 --> 00:35:40,168
You bastard! Answer my questions!

466
00:35:40,168 --> 00:35:44,049
What did you do to Xi Gua? Where is she now?

467
00:35:44,049 --> 00:35:48,789
Badao Camp is still safe.

468
00:35:49,710 --> 00:35:54,889
They should be hiding somewhere in the mountains.

469
00:35:56,190 --> 00:35:58,510
There is no need to worry.

470
00:35:58,510 --> 00:36:02,789
I came here today to ask you a few questions.

471
00:36:03,570 --> 00:36:08,170
What a coincidence! I also have a few for you.

472
00:36:08,750 --> 00:36:14,230
Did someone tell you to attack Lin'an?

473
00:36:14,230 --> 00:36:15,109
Yes.

474
00:36:15,109 --> 00:36:20,309
Did you come here to prevent the army from heading north?

475
00:36:20,309 --> 00:36:22,109
Yes.

476
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:29,469
How did you know that there would be a downpour this morning?

477
00:36:30,929 --> 00:36:32,770
Well,

478
00:36:33,389 --> 00:36:36,509
I didn't actually.

479
00:36:36,509 --> 00:36:40,329
Lin'an has a lot of rainfall. I was just waiting.

480
00:36:40,329 --> 00:36:41,408
Waiting?

481
00:36:41,408 --> 00:36:43,289
I was waiting for the rain.

482
00:36:43,289 --> 00:36:47,729
The rain was the signal to attack Lin'an.

483
00:36:50,029 --> 00:36:52,670
So, I'm doomed.

484
00:36:52,670 --> 00:36:54,750
One last question,

485
00:36:54,750 --> 00:36:56,570
Fang Tian Lei.

486
00:36:57,049 --> 00:37:01,510
The person who ordered you to prevent the army from heading north,

487
00:37:01,510 --> 00:37:03,029
who is it?

488
00:37:05,330 --> 00:37:09,350
Dong Dao Fu also asked me this.

489
00:37:09,350 --> 00:37:11,489
My answer is still the same.

490
00:37:11,489 --> 00:37:17,029
If I don't tell you, what can you do to me?

491
00:37:18,389 --> 00:37:19,910
Just leave, Ning Yi.

492
00:37:19,910 --> 00:37:23,960
You will never get to know the answer to this question.

493
00:37:26,210 --> 00:37:30,310
Waiting for the rain. Excellent!

494
00:37:49,210 --> 00:37:54,980
[Wudu]

495
00:37:57,569 --> 00:38:00,630
Urgent report from the front line.

496
00:38:03,710 --> 00:38:05,629
Your Majesty. Urgent report from the front line.

497
00:38:05,629 --> 00:38:08,188
- Read it now, quickly!
- Yes.

498
00:38:09,030 --> 00:38:12,110
General Dong Dao Fu has taken Lin'an back.

499
00:38:12,110 --> 00:38:15,309
The Secret Investigation Department cooperated from the inside with the people outside.

500
00:38:15,309 --> 00:38:18,469
Commander Ning Li Heng carried out an excellent plan

501
00:38:18,469 --> 00:38:21,949
to make Fang Tian Lei, the head of the bandits, fail to use the gunpowder.

502
00:38:21,949 --> 00:38:26,529
They've not only kept the people of Lin'an safe but also won the time to take back the city.

503
00:38:26,529 --> 00:38:30,429
On Sept. 19th, the fifth year of Jinghan's reign, Lin'an was recovered.

504
00:38:30,429 --> 00:38:34,610
Fang Tian Lei, the head of the bandits, was captured alive.

505
00:38:36,130 --> 00:38:40,668
Minister, there is something that's been troubling me.

506
00:38:41,389 --> 00:38:47,329
I think if Fang Tian Lei comes to the capital, he will cause you trouble.

507
00:38:47,329 --> 00:38:51,750
Do you want me to send someone to kill him instead?

508
00:38:52,650 --> 00:38:54,750
No need.

509
00:38:54,750 --> 00:38:57,289
Once Lin'an is taken,

510
00:38:57,289 --> 00:39:00,408
Fang Tian Lei will become useless.

511
00:39:00,408 --> 00:39:03,389
How much trouble can he cause?

512
00:39:03,389 --> 00:39:08,789
Let him be. I have more important things to do.

513
00:39:13,290 --> 00:39:15,090
Minister He,

514
00:39:15,670 --> 00:39:18,730
His Majesty wants to see you.

515
00:39:20,750 --> 00:39:24,348
His Majesty ordered Dong Dao Fu to lead 100,000 troops due south.

516
00:39:24,348 --> 00:39:27,549
Lin'an had been recovered. The bandits had been eliminated.

517
00:39:27,549 --> 00:39:31,428
Fang Tian Lei, the head of the bandits and his followers were all arrested.

518
00:39:31,428 --> 00:39:34,368
They would be executed in a few days. This was the moment for celebration.

519
00:39:34,368 --> 00:39:36,309
This is a dynasty with all the people of one mind.

520
00:39:36,309 --> 00:39:39,789
Great. Excellent.

521
00:39:49,230 --> 00:39:53,469
God bless! Great!

522
00:39:53,469 --> 00:39:55,830
Now Bo Yong is in good health.

523
00:39:55,830 --> 00:39:58,010
And Tan'er and Ning Yi will be back soon, too.

524
00:39:58,010 --> 00:40:01,389
I... I'm going to the temple to offer prayers.

525
00:40:01,389 --> 00:40:05,749
You should stay home. Maybe they'll be back in a minute.

526
00:40:05,749 --> 00:40:07,349
That's right.

527
00:40:07,349 --> 00:40:11,648
Well. Then I'll prepare some food and drinks that they like.

528
00:40:11,648 --> 00:40:12,930
We'll give them a warm welcome.

529
00:40:12,930 --> 00:40:14,269
Yeah, that's right.

530
00:40:14,269 --> 00:40:15,769
Let's go.

531
00:40:29,929 --> 00:40:31,529
Father, look.

532
00:40:31,529 --> 00:40:33,970
This is our family's cloth store.

533
00:40:35,330 --> 00:40:38,669
Look at you!

534
00:40:54,009 --> 00:40:59,089
Look. The eighth branch of Zhu Restaurant.

535
00:40:59,089 --> 00:41:03,170
In the blink of an eye, so many stores have been opened.

536
00:41:03,170 --> 00:41:07,529
I really didn't expect that we would come back alive.

537
00:41:10,569 --> 00:41:14,909
Well, I am really starting to miss my wife.

538
00:41:14,909 --> 00:41:18,389
The days that we can argue and fight were so great.

539
00:41:18,389 --> 00:41:21,170
Yet I didn't cherish them.

540
00:41:21,909 --> 00:41:25,509
I wonder if my wife is in good health now.

541
00:41:25,509 --> 00:41:29,130
We left here so long ago, yet we didn't even bring any gifts.

542
00:41:29,130 --> 00:41:32,409
The husband's safe return is enough to comfort his wife.

543
00:41:32,409 --> 00:41:37,749
Now that you came back safely, this could be the greatest gift to your wives.

544
00:41:37,749 --> 00:41:39,810
Good for you, Shen Miao.

545
00:41:39,810 --> 00:41:45,209
After this trip to Lin'an, your insights into love have grown.

546
00:41:46,150 --> 00:41:51,248
People who've experienced life and death will change their opinions about earthly life.

547
00:41:53,449 --> 00:41:54,849
What are you doing?

548
00:41:54,849 --> 00:41:57,810
I think we are still dreaming.

549
00:41:57,810 --> 00:41:59,988
Shut up! Close your mouth!

550
00:41:59,988 --> 00:42:03,689
Elder Master. Elder Master.

551
00:42:03,689 --> 00:42:07,028
Elder Master. Lady and Young Master have come back!

552
00:42:07,028 --> 00:42:10,928
Excellent! Excellent!

553
00:42:13,989 --> 00:42:15,689
Let's go!

554
00:42:22,090 --> 00:42:24,350
[Su Manor]

555
00:42:28,030 --> 00:42:29,530
Mother.

556
00:42:29,530 --> 00:42:31,689
I've missed you so much!

557
00:42:31,689 --> 00:42:35,048
I've looked forward to your return all this time. You're finally back!

558
00:42:35,048 --> 00:42:37,229
