- Grandfather!

560
00:42:38,668 --> 00:42:41,369
I'm great! We're okay. Don't worry about us.

561
00:42:41,369 --> 00:42:42,449
Father!

562
00:42:42,449 --> 00:42:44,108
Grandfather! Grandfather!

563
00:42:44,108 --> 00:42:46,929
